FBIS4-47965 "drafr089_e_94001" FBIS-AFR-94-089 Daily Report 6 May 1994 WEST AFRICA Benin Soglo Appoints New Minister of Justice, Legislation Soglo Appoints New Minister of Justice, Legislation AB0605223594 Cotonou Office de Radiodiffusion-Television du Benin Radio in French 1930 GMT 6 May 94 AB0605223594 Cotonou Office de Radiodiffusion-Television du Benin Radio French BFN [Text] The cabinet has been altered in Benin. Nicephore Soglo, president of the Republic and head of state and government, appointed (Pierre Nevi) minister of justice and legislation today in place of Yves Yehouessi. The new minister of justice and legislation is a member of Joseph Adjignon Keke's National Rally for Democracy.
